## 五、改进建议

### 5.1 架构改进

#### 1. 事件驱动架构
```typescript
// events/event-bus.ts
export class EventBus {
  private listeners = new Map<string, Function[]>();

  on(event: string, handler: Function) {
    if (!this.listeners.has(event)) {
      this.listeners.set(event, []);
    }
    this.listeners.get(event)!.push(handler);
  }

  emit(event: string, data: any) {
    this.listeners.get(event)?.forEach(handler => handler(data));
  }
}

// 使用
eventBus.on('iteration.started', (data) => {
  iterationService.create(data);
  realtimeService.broadcast('iteration.started', data);
});
```

#### 2. Agent 状态机
```typescript
// agents/agent-state-machine.ts
export enum AgentStatus {
  IDLE = 'idle',
  RUNNING = 'running',
  SUCCESS = 'success',
  FAILED = 'failed'
}

export class AgentStateMachine {
  private status: AgentStatus = AgentStatus.IDLE;

  start() { this.status = AgentStatus.RUNNING; }
  complete() { this.status = AgentStatus.SUCCESS; }
  fail() { this.status = AgentStatus.FAILED; }
}
```

---

### 5.2 性能优化

#### 1. 历史记录压缩
```typescript
// base-agent.ts
private saveHistoryToFile(): void {
  const compressed = this.fullHistory.map(h => ({
    r: h.role[0], // role -> 'u'/'a'
    c: h.content.substring(0, 100), // content -> 前100字符
    t: h.timestamp.getTime()
  }));

  fs.writeFile(this.historyFile, JSON.stringify(compressed));
}
```

#### 2. Agent 并行池
```typescript
// auto-iteration.ts
private async executeInPool(agents: BaseAgent[], task: string) {
  const pool = new PromisePool({ concurrency: 3 }); // 最多3个并行
  return pool.map(agents, agent => agent.executeAndCollect(task));
}
```

---

### 5.3 测试与质量

#### 1. 单元测试
```typescript
