```

#### 2. E2E 测试
```typescript
// tests/e2e/iteration.test.ts
test('should complete one iteration', async () => {
  const engine = new AutoIterationEngine({
    maxIterations: 1,
    autoCommit: false,
    autoPush: false
  });

  await engine.start();
  expect(engine.getIterationCount()).toBe(1);
});
```

